            </h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-300 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
              Transform your space into a private retreat. These homeowner designs use layering and dense planting to achieve a professional jungle look that you can plant yourself. Get inspired to turn your yard into a personal paradise using Hadaa's visualization tools.
